ultrabay-scripts (0.14-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Removed thinkpad_check function from ultrabay_common file and all
    scripts using it. This check was too specific and unnecessarily
    excluded older Thinkpad models like the T23. Checking for the
    presence of a valid tp_smapi installation should be enough.

