ultrabay-scripts (0.11-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Renamed variable "dock" to "DOCKDEV", and "battery" to "BATDEV"
    for better overview.

  * Added "Recommends: tlp, acpi-call-source, acpi-call-tools" in
    control file.

  * Corrected erroneous UDEV_PATH detection and inprecise UBDEV
    definition in ultrabay_common file.

  * Rewrote the init script in order to check for the presence of the
    ata_piix module, which is required for basic UltraBay functionality
    on various ThinkPad models.

  * Updated the README.Debian file to reflect the most current status.

 -- Window Maker Live <wmlive@users.sf.net>  Sat, 11 May 2013 21:19:44 +0200

